   <conbody>
      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">In float charge operation the rectifier supplies the load
and charges the battery with the float voltage setting.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The
rectifier mains input feeds the phase angle controlled rectifier with
a galvanically isolated transformer and converts the AC to DC. The
rectifier regulation maintains the set float voltage for input voltage
variations and various DC loads.</p>
